oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Carl Smith at the El Paso County Coliseum (18182)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Smith, Carl, 1927-2010;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing Carl Smith with Harry Blanton and Cliff Seaman at the El Paso County Coliseum on December 4. Poster features a metal photoplate of Carl Smith. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/25451.
